data.description: Step into your dream home  in this hard to find, 5 bedroom, 2 bathroom haven! Meticulously upgraded, featuring recently renovated kitchen, luxurious bathrooms, and gleaming floors highlighted by newer paint. Enjoy the convenience of a indoor laundry,  solar panels and updated heating and air conditioning. The spacious backyard and front and rear covered porches offer perfect relaxation spots, complemented by the practicality of an oversized 2 car detached garage. This home is not just a property; it's a lifestyle waiting to be embraced, whether you desire an entertainer's delight or a family hangout. Don't miss the chance to claim this Home as yours. Visit today and start your journey to homeownership.  Upcoming Lincoln Park and Pomona are sought after not just by professionals, but artists, and historical preservationists, yet with family friendly vide.  Also, near public trans, downtown Regional Trans hub, 2 Metrolink stations, 4 freeways, Cal Poly Pomona, Western U., Claremont Colleges, University of La Verne, Pomona’s award-winning schools and Pomona Valley Trauma Center. PLUS, the L Line, is coming to Pomona. You're close to Stater Bros, Cardenas, Smart & Final, and the legendary Glass House, Fox Theater, the world famous Fairplex with its renowned Children’s Learning Center and the ever-popular annual LA County Fair. Your dream home awaits – seize the opportunity today!
